  <brief_title>Identifying Characteristic Signature of Attention Deficit / Hyperactivity Disorder (ADHD) and Ritalin Treatment</brief_title>
  <official_title>Identifying Characteristic Signature of Brain Activity of Electroencephalogram Records in Attention Deficit / Hyperactivity Disorder (ADHD) and Ritalin Treatment</official_title>
